room_title: Escape room "Shipwreck Cove" by Headzup in Las Vegas
room_address: 3542 S Maryland Parkway Las Vegas, NV 89169
room_description: The “Cursed Treasure” Pirate Ship has been lost at sea for many years, and you are the first to stumbled upon it while on your ocean adventure. Legend has it, hidden treasure was left behind, but to get to it you must first explore the island. Can you find the treasure before someone else does?
